{"tid":1467854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住 捉鬼並非重點","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:03.000Z","uid":138809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe199eabe6e76cbe5d29fb7e3013851098e33ce","tid":1467854,"uid":138809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"畀你捉到又點? <br />\n好容易畀人帶到風向"},{"pid":"061a15594cd763e2851295b3072ef0dd3db6ce18","tid":1467854,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9591a572251f79d9a6e7230dfc245f58252ff6","tid":1467854,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"不割蓆已經由我地嘅優勢變成劣勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b2c6b08b740bc49aca84adca08ae6c0487043da","tid":1467854,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係要捉地佢出黎<br />\n但大家要認到鬼<br />\n有獨立思考<br />\n唔好人講就跟<br />\n帶到大家失哂理智</span></span>"},{"pid":"0d94d88e476d3f9186764a3ee33ca3c61b35467f","tid":1467854,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不足鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"}]}